0a%3c %0a%3c The Speakeasy is truly the one crowning achievement of Remy's, and it's seen it's fair share of use throughout the years.  From the smuggler tunnels that lead around parts of the city to allow access with secret panels, to the shop above it, Remy's taken his time to care for it properly, to the point one would imagine that it was his first love.  Parties, events, meetings, debates, negotiations...  All manner of things occur here, and Remy loves the fact that he can help it happen there.  In ages long gone, the Rose City Guild met there on occasion, a place to discuss things where there were rules, but not laws.  It continues on to this day, with Remy watching over the place and the proceedings with the keen eye of a man who loves the place with all his heart.%0a%3c ----%0a%3c %0a%3c !! Contacts%0a%3c %0a%3c (:table table border=0 cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0:)%0a%3c %0a%3c (:cellnr width=360px:) %25lfloat width=150%25 https://i.imgur.com/Licu228.jpg%0a%3c [[EssenceCorvin| Essie]] and [[VerbenaPoemLarson| Verbena]]\\%0a%3c %25white%25 Nearly everyone knows that Remy is madly in love with the two women, and he most certainly lavishes all the attention he can on the two of them.%0a%3c %0a%3c (:cell width=360px:) %25lfloat width=150%25 https://i.imgur.com/HAwa3nf.jpg%0a%3c [[LoreleiBowen | Lorelei]]\\%0a%3c %25white%25 Remy has a soft spot a mile long for Lorelei, and it shows in the way that he drops most things to help her out, if she needs it.  Very good friends indeed.%0a%3c %0a%3c (:cellnr width=360px:) %25lfloat width=150%25 https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/fox-thegifted/images/f/f2/BTS_1x05_Boxed_In_Emma_Dumont_%2527Magneto_gesture%2527.jpg%0a%3c [[AriaAetherRockefeller | Aria]]\\%0a%3c %25white%25 The two of them met by him giving her a ride home when she had too much to drink.  SInce then, they keep running into each other, all over town.%0a%3c %0a%3c (:cell width=360px:) %25lfloat width=150%25 https://i.pinimg.com/736x/b5/ca/ab/b5caabb5261d0bcd